@node how "How will use it?"

  To use this program it is necessary install it in your hard disk,
also you need the serial  number to be able to use him; because the
Eye Viewer  is not free;  it is giftware.  The serial number are of
two types  standard  and full.  The serial number  for the standard
version  allow  you to see  unlimited photos  but not to  listen to
sounds; with the serail  number for the  full version  allow you to
see and to listen to images and sounds unlimited.
 We prune to be exploring our hard disk until will find some drawer
with photos;  and once  it will show us  a list of  the photos that
Eye Viewer  find in it;  in spite  of pulsating  in the name of the
photo  automatically  it will  show us the  photo which we prune to
choose  that  shows  it  to us  in  size  real or  adapted  to  the
resolution  of our screen,  which we  will be able  to choose if we
choose for  that it  shows the  photos on an  own screen of the Eye
Viewer.


Evolutions and improvements of the Eye Viewer:

  The innovation of the version 2.1:
   - Added the  possibility of  using other datatypes  besides them
     original of Amiga OS.
   - Added  the  option   to  choose  smoothed  only  availably  in
     graphical mode of 8 bits.
   - Corrected a  bug in the  option of search  of files that in OS
     4.0 it was provoking its hangs.
   - Change the graph and the animation in the menu "About" for one
     only standard and definitive animation.

 The innovation of the version 2.0:
  - When setting the pointer on oversize pictures you can also move
    up and down, left and right with a click on the left mouse key.
  - Zoom for increase or dimish one image, with the keys + and -.
  - Search one image for its name.
  - Mirror option we can rotation one image vertical or horizontal.


 The innovation of the version 1.2:
  - Correction of bugs.
  - The installer now  allows to install the new  languages without
    it need to have to return to install the program again.

 The innovation of the version 1.1:
  - Now we  can displace with  arrows keys up or down for the names
    of the  images  and  automaticly it  is  show into  of the left
    window.
  - With  Enter key you can  ajust the  image a its real size or to
    scale.

@endnode

